  ID: MenAtArms
  Name: Portuguese swordsman
  Icon: {fileID: -487541979, guid: cb9f5804ad6456a4f9a2ba7a478c3f60, type: 3}
  Description: 'He chased duels like other men chase gold. On the wall, a snapped
    blade slid between his ribs and stayed lodged like a metal rib. Every breath
    trembles.


    Treatment: Enlarge the wound only enough to grip steel. Remove
    the fragment slowly. Seal with cautery if bleeding persists. Binding his chest
    may delay the inevitable.


    Requires: 2 Bandages'
